{"tid":1047512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大民主牆風波　超超超超懶人包","createTime":"2019-03-05T04:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T04:13:25.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"adebf0a3828e68815452739a1d87fb357f6b4338","tid":1047512,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1043784/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1043784/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n理大學生紀律委員會<br />\n<br />\n成員 <strong>莫志明 理大學務長／教授測量師</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lsgi.polyu.edu.hk/_images/people/academic/mok-chi-ming.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lsgi.polyu.edu.hk%2F_images%2Fpeople%2Facademic%2Fmok-chi-ming.jpg&h=390a237c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1）理大學務長莫志明要求理大學生會在24小時內把民主牆恢復原狀，否則將沒收民主牆<br />\n2）及後<span style=\"color: red;\">民主牆遭學校保安用中國國旗覆蓋</span><br />\n3）三個月後，理大學生會前往高層辦公室理論，理大學務長莫志明在混亂中插水，學生上前扶起，莫志明指「會原諒學生整親佢隻腳」<br />\n<br />\n原本民主牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211207_b2919b936a302d445426e2dcc631f702.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211207_b2919b936a302d445426e2dcc631f702.png&h=a2af3b62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來民主牆（ 議事論事 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/legcoreview/posts/1929369657118316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flegcoreview%2Fposts%2F1929369657118316&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=7ca25ead\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/legcoreview/posts/1929369657118316</a> ）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211205_7de4b56e5e760b7c1cf7c8baa609fa8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211205_7de4b56e5e760b7c1cf7c8baa609fa8d.jpg&h=b79d0361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211203_6ac8fb69624e0c3ff719f2784f1dffb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211203_6ac8fb69624e0c3ff719f2784f1dffb1.jpg&h=e3d1ee62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211204_5ca9b91400d5f2190aa1dff18c506556.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211204_5ca9b91400d5f2190aa1dff18c506556.jpg&h=1244e70b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［我會原諒你事件］（網上圖片及文字）<br />\n混亂中，教授突然單腳跌在地上，何同學即時上前扶起，緊張地問：「你有無事？有無事？需唔需要搵個地方坐低？」<br />\n<br />\n教授猶豫了一陣，表示沒事，並用手搭著何同學膊頭，連聲表示「我會原諒你」、「我會原諒你」，何同學卻向對方說：「我唔係要你原諒我，我係唔會原諒校方打壓民主自由！」<br />\n<br />\n教授隨即澄清：「我係話我會原諒你整親我隻腳」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211443_00fb7f2091cff6afb826ded61cd6049a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211443_00fb7f2091cff6afb826ded61cd6049a.jpg&h=ad91b3c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理大學生紀律委員會指控涉事學生4項罪名，包括出言譴責時任暫任副校長（學生事務）沈岐平和學務長莫志明，「你哋收共產黨錢收得咁過癮，舐共舐得你哋咁開心呀啦，屎忽鬼」，被指誹謗成立。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/212636_abf50fe0959ef12424c987aa1cc66aa9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F212636_abf50fe0959ef12424c987aa1cc66aa9.png&h=44eefea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員 <strong>陳炳泉 建築及房地產學系教授</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/web/filemanager/polyumainmediarelease/en/upload/2308/20120531202202_IMG_2_resize.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fweb%2Ffilemanager%2Fpolyumainmediarelease%2Fen%2Fupload%2F2308%2F20120531202202_IMG_2_resize.JPG&h=b95da652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映 <strong>時任理大大學校長 第十二屆、第十三屆全國政協委員 唐偉章</strong><br />\n著名中聯辦組織香港青年大專學生協會 及 香港新一代文化協會 榮譽顧問<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.newgen.org.hk/wp-content/uploads/bfi_thumb/20101030135533i-nkla51vxtapzkdrbqcxni2ja4o0yqmr51eao0rdybw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newgen.org.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fbfi_thumb%2F20101030135533i-nkla51vxtapzkdrbqcxni2ja4o0yqmr51eao0rdybw.jpg&h=e02d45ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理工大學去年10月初發生民主牆風波，理大學生紀律委員會昨日召開聆訊後，分別勒令4人退學、停學或須履行社會服務令。理大前校長<strong>唐偉章</strong>表示，對前同事有信心，並指相信校方相關人員是經過謹慎考慮才作出決定，對裁決毫無疑問。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（網上文字）<br />\n<br />\n查既係其中五個委員加一個學生<br />\n咁實際上有冇學生代表參與委員會，定係得五個professor決定？<br />\n<br />\n學生會長2/28退任<br />\n1/3宣布紀律聆訊結果<br />\n理大係咪特登等到學生會長退任，冇得參與冇票<br />\n先出結果先？"}]}